       DEF  COLHRZ
	   
* Return true if the specified 
* rectangle is directly above or 
* overlaping a horizontal line
*
COLHRZ 
* Move uppper-left corner of sprite into R0
	   MOV  *R0,R0
* Move left-most point of line into R2
	   MOV  *R2,R2
* Erase x-coordinate and leave only
* y-coordinate behind in R0 and R2
	   SRL  R0,8
	   SRL  R2,8
* If value in R0 <= R2,
* return true (collision detected)
	   C    R0,R2
	   JLE  COLH1
       CLR  R4
       RT
COLH1  SETO R4
       RT

       END